This document describes file organisation of the Human-Robot Interaction part of the CONCEPT project.

./		high-level information, startup script
common/		common (and hopefully reusable) python modules and utilities
HRI/		main python modules and utilities
HRI/face/	display engine (Blender) and client interfaces
HRI/gaze/	gazing dynamics, postures (eg: thinking -> gazing up) and iris
HRI/vision/	set of image processing modules (color/edge/face/expression detection)
HRI/neck/	head movements (dynamics, postures, IK)
HRI/affect/	affective module (emotion, mood, personality)
HRI/dynamics/	motion dynamics (movement functions for other modules)
interface/	interface modules for the concept learning part (other repository)
experiments/	default directory for specific code and results
